    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting go of this burden\"... what does that even mean? you say it like it's some kind of peaceful conclusion. but it feels like there's no way to just walk away from this. my identity, my whole sense of who i am, was tied to being right. now i'm just... nothing. just an empty space where a person used to be.",
