    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple. the pressure doesn't just go away because i stop working. everyone expects something from me. my colleagues, my family... they see the person i was. if i just \"let go,\" i'm still stuck in this world, dealing with the shame of everything i've ruined. is there actually an end to it? or do i just keep living with this hollow version of myself forever?",
